## About Laravel

Laravel is a web application framework with expressive, elegant syntax. We believe development must be an enjoyable and creative experience to be truly fulfilling. Laravel takes the pain out of development by easing common tasks used in many web projects, such as:

- [Simple, fast routing engine](https://laravel.com/docs/routing).
- [Powerful dependency injection container](https://laravel.com/docs/container).
- Multiple back-ends for [session](https://laravel.com/docs/session) and [cache](https://laravel.com/docs/cache) storage.
- Expressive, intuitive [database ORM](https://laravel.com/docs/eloquent).
- Database agnostic [schema migrations](https://laravel.com/docs/migrations).
- [Robust background job processing](https://laravel.com/docs/queues).
- [Real-time event broadcasting](https://laravel.com/docs/broadcasting).

Laravel is accessible, powerful, and provides tools required for large, robust applications.

## Learning Laravel

Laravel has the most extensive and thorough [documentation](https://laravel.com/docs) and video tutorial library of all modern web application frameworks, making it a breeze to get started with the framework.

You may also try the [Laravel Bootcamp](https://bootcamp.laravel.com), where you will be guided through building a modern Laravel application from scratch.

If you don't feel like reading, [Laracasts](https://laracasts.com) can help. Laracasts contains thousands of video tutorials on a range of topics including Laravel, modern PHP, unit testing, and JavaScript. Boost your skills by digging into our comprehensive video library.

  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `title_english` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `title_vietnamese` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `transcription` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `type` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT 'vocabulary',
  `sound` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `means` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT 'vocabulary',
  `result_users` text,
  `created_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `deleted_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `FK_lesson_details_lessions` (`lesson_id`),
  CONSTRAINT `FK_lesson_details_lessions` FOREIGN KEY (`lesson_id`) REFERENCES `lessons` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=758 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

  `title_english` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci NOT NULL,
  `title_vietnamese` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci NOT NULL,
  `lesson_detail_id` int NOT NULL,
  `answer` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'CHOOSE',
  `game_detail_id` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `deleted_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `FK_questions_lesson_details` (`lesson_detail_id`),
  KEY `FK_questions_game_details` (`game_detail_id`),
  CONSTRAINT `FK_questions_game_details` FOREIGN KEY (`game_detail_id`) REFERENCES `game_details` (`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `FK_questions_lesson_details` FOREIGN KEY (`lesson_detail_id`) REFERENCES `lesson_details` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7363 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

	(7050, 'Đọc bài sau và trả lời các câu hỏi: Hello, everyone. My name is An, and I\'m currently a third-year university student majoring in Information Technology (IT). I\'m 21 years old and I live in Hanoi, Vietnam.  I chose IT because I have a deep interest in problem-solving and the way technology is constantly shaping our world. I particularly enjoy coding and working on small web development projects in my spare time. My goal after graduation is to become a software engineer and contribute to innovative tech solutions.  Outside of my studies, I have a few hobbies that keep me balanced. My main passion is photography, especially capturing street scenes and candid moments. It allows me to observe the world from a different perspective. I also enjoy playing badminton with my friends on weekends, which is a great way to stay active and relieve stress.  I consider myself a diligent, curious, and collaborative person. I\'m always eager to learn new things, whether it\'s a new programming language or a new photography technique. I believe that effective communication and teamwork are crucial for success in any field.
